Options -Indexes

# We REMOVED the "Require all denied" for setup_db.php

# so that you can actually run it to set up your database.

# Security headers

<IfModule mod_headers.c>
    Header always set X-Content-Type-Options "nosniff"
    Header always set X-Frame-Options "SAMEORIGIN"
    Header always set X-XSS-Protection "1; mode=block"
    Header always set Referrer-Policy "strict-origin-when-cross-origin"
</IfModule>

# To prevent PHP execution in the uploads folder,

# you should put a separate .htaccess file INSIDE the uploads folder.

# The <Directory> tag is NOT allowed here, so I have removed it.
